  "description": "The plaintiff brought a lawsuit in the  Fresno Superior Court in Glendale bearing case number EC 021473 against our clients for assault, battery, and intentional infliction of emotional distress. The plaintiff sought $25,000 in compensatory damages and punitive damages against our client. Essentially, the plaintiff claimed that our client assaulted and battered him in a fight that occurred in the Mann Theater in Glendale, California. The plaintiff also sued the theater for allegedly negligently providing security. Our clients brought a cross-complaint against the theater for indemnity and contribution and against the plaintiff for assault, battery, and intentional infliction of...",
